about.summary: Python parser for the Shuttle Radar Topography Mission elevation data.

name: srtm.py
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.3.1" %}

package:
    name: srtm.py
    version: {{ version }}

source:
    fn: SRTM.py-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    url: https://github.com/tkrajina/srtm.py/archive/v.{{ version }}.tar.gz
    sha256: 00d58962e991c7d633f65843078b0e1f8e7f534ac1ddfd8c049effcd331ef6ad

build:
    number: 0
    skip: True  # [py3k]
    script: python setup.py install

requirements:
    build:
        - python
    run:
        - python
        - requests
        - gpxpy

test:
    imports:
        - srtm
    commands:
        - gpxelevations -h

about:
    home: https://github.com/tkrajina/srtm.py
    license: Apache 2.0
    summary: 'Python parser for the Shuttle Radar Topography Mission elevation data.'

extra:
    recipe-maintainers:
        - ocefpaf
